sentences: Charles Mariano Robinson (born February 2, 1984) is a music video and commercial director, and musician.
Robinson is known for shooting videos for artists such as Waka Flocka, Young Buck, and Shawty Lo.
Robinson attended Greenbelt Middle School in Greenbelt, Maryland and attended Fairmont Heights High School (Maryland) in Capitol Heights, Maryland.
